name: Godje
description: ’Godje‘ is a animation made while preparing an exhibition at Ghent for the Orpheus Institute. Thematically it is close to ‘Guru’ and technically it is based on a Flash New Year card from 2007. In 2015 a new version was renamed to 'Burner'. 2009 CR 585 https://hansup.be/2009_godje_animation_hans-verhaegen.html
